201.name: Meet Goku
201.des: You wake up in unknown yet familiar place. A young girl is standing next to you.

202.name: New Journey
202.des: You meet an old man on a turtle shell. He's said to be a martial arts master.

203.name: Yamcha's Back
203.des: Yamcha just came back to give you a car. Didn't that guy try to attack us before?!

204.name: Training
204.des: The Island is not far away. We are ready to be trained by Master Roshi.

205.name: 21st Games
205.des: We finally arrived in the city! Everything here is so flashy and new!

206.name: Muscle Tower
206.des: Goku sets out to find his grandpa's Dragon Ball. Let's go!

207.name: General Blue
207.des: That darn radar broke. We need to find Bulma to help us fix it.

208.name: Assassin
208.des: The Radar shows the Dragon ball is near that big pillar. We've got to find it before the Red Ribbon Army comes!

209.name: Crystal Ball
209.des: The Radar is unable to detect the last Dragon Ball. Let's ask Fortuneteller Baba to help us!

210.name: 22nd Games
210.des: Time for our second Tournament! Goku, Jackie and Krillin are ready to fight!

211.name: King Piccolo
211.des: Who killed Krillin? Why is Master Roshi so serious? What's this familiar smell?

212.name: Temple
212.des: Yajirobe arrived just in time to save us! That was close. We really should train harder!

213.name: 23rd Games
213.des: Everyone changed so much! Let's go and test our powers!

214.name: Garlic Jr.
214.des: Piccolo, Gohan, Chi-Chi and the Ox king were attacked! We've got to stop these bandits!

215.name: Dr. Wheelo
215.des: The Dragon Balls are appearing across the Northern Glaciers. Oolong and Gohan encounter something quite unexpected.

216.name: Goku Dies
216.des: A UFO just landed on earth! This alien doesn't seem interested in a peaceful chat with the locals.

217.name: Vegeta
217.des: Two more villains arrive after Raditz's death. They are more powerful than King Kai! Will we be able to defeat them?

218.name: Namek
218.des: Piccolo has died and Vegeta has disappeared. Krillin, Gohan and Bulma want to revive their friends by going to Namek.

219.name: Ginyu Force
219.des: The Elder tells them more powerful enemies has arrived. Gohan, Krillin and Vegeta have to face unknown enemies.

220.name: Lord Frieza
220.des: Emperor Frieza is here! Goku is still healing. Can Vegeta, Gohan and Krillin stop him?

221.name: Makyo
221.des: Kami hoped Piccolo would be his successor. Piccolo however warns us for enemies in the future.

222.name: Revenge
222.des: A mysterious Super Saiyan predicts the comeback of Goku and warns us for evil yet to come.

223.name: Best vs Best
223.des: We thought the Frieza Legion was defeated! This new army is unbelievable!

224.name: Android Raid
224.des: That's it for now! What will the future hold in store for our heroes? Just wait and see!

225.name: Cell's Game
225.des: Cell's lecture creates fear and panic all over the world.

226.name: Pirate Bojack
226.des: At the birthday party there are really alien races!

227.name: Lord Slug
227.des: Old Slug won't give up the destruction. He is ready to invade the earth

228.name: Hell Game
228.des: Hell Game is on!  Goku VS Pikkon!

229.name: Janemba
229.des: The Soul Cleansing Machine exploded! Janemba begins to turn Hell into his own paradise.

230.name: Dragon Fist
230.des: Hirudegarn appears on earth.Sayans! Roll out!
